Package: SPER
Title: Calculate Spatial Paired Expression Ratio
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tianxiao", "Zhao", , "tianxiao_zhao@hsph.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package is designed to calculate the SPER scores in spatial transcriptomics analysis. Users can use these scores to evaluate the spatial dependence, especially a paracrine-pattern, between a gene and a targeting cell types. 
